{"tid":899964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"￼波蘭慶祝獨立100周年 極右團體參加首都遊行","createTime":"2018-11-13T00:55:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T01:04:20.000Z","uid":75610,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e51d3c554955f70607856f59675869a2743670e9","tid":899964,"uid":75610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T00:55:18.000Z","msg":"波蘭周日（11日）慶祝獨立100周年，總統杜達（Andrzej Duda）帶領逾20萬民眾，包括極右民族主義團體，於首都華沙參加遊行；大部分參加者手持波蘭國旗並穿載紅白臂章，部分人則高舉代表波蘭和意大利右翼政黨的橫額。<br />\n總統杜達在遊行開始時向民眾發表講話，感謝民眾參與遊行，稱波蘭紅白國旗見證前人所灑的血：「在我們的旗幟下，每個人都有自己的位置。」政府官員與主要遊行隊伍保持一定距離，遠離民族主義相關顯著標示，並由保安人員分隔開，反對派則杯葛遊行。<br />\n<br />\n有參與遊行的民眾高呼「遠離歐盟」，但未有如往年出現白人優越主義的橫幅，部分人手持寫有「上帝、榮譽、祖國」的橫幅，又有人發射紅色火光，煙霧覆蓋部分遊行隊伍；另有參加者高叫口號「昨天莫斯科，今日布魯塞爾，剝奪主權。」<br />\n<br />\n自執政黨法律與正義黨（PiS）2015年上台後，波蘭逐漸在歐洲變得孤立，外界有指波蘭慢慢趨向極權統治。華沙市長一直尋求禁止極右團體在每年11月11日的獨立日遊行，但不獲法院接納，政府其後與主辦團體達成協議聯合舉辦遊行。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/257819/%E6%B3%A2%E8%98%AD%E6%85%B6%E7%A5%9D%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B100%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4-%E6%A5%B5%E5%8F%B3%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E5%8F%83%E5%8A%A0%E9%A6%96%E9%83%BD%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2F257819%2F%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E8%2598%25AD%25E6%2585%25B6%25E7%25A5%259D%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B100%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25B9%25B4-%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E5%258F%25B3%25E5%259C%2598%25E9%25AB%2594%25E5%258F%2583%25E5%258A%25A0%25E9%25A6%2596%25E9%2583%25BD%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C&d=SsN2fCzZsuJIJ9cIHCIj4TPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=c9f447fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/257819/%E6%B3%A2%E8%98%AD%E6%85%B6%E7%A5%9D%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B100%E5%91%A8%E5%B9%B4-%E6%A5%B5%E5%8F%B3%E5%9C%98%E9%AB%94%E5%8F%83%E5%8A%A0%E9%A6%96%E9%83%BD%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C</a>"},{"pid":"fa51b9abf1631d6ecb7cbd2b4f595146f593e044","tid":899964,"uid":75610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T00:55:55.000Z","msg":"極你老母權 支那01<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c4f35ae756399d335997ffb418ae59d5ea7de2","tid":899964,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T00:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thisblogishappyend.files.wordpress.com/2011/09/obama-witcher-feature.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthisblogishappyend.files.wordpress.com%2F2011%2F09%2Fobama-witcher-feature.jpg&h=fbff1e9e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"241f0890af93636d90c071eca3dda9721bc85615","tid":899964,"uid":75610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T01:04:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B05NxQw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB05NxQw.png&h=a11b1998&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n右翼旗 個logo應該係波蘭falangist"}]}